      "name": "Parameters",
      "description": "input(Tensor) – the input tensor. Must be at least 2-dimensional.offset(int,optional) – which diagonal to consider. Default: 0\n(main diagonal).dim1(int,optional) – first dimension with respect to which to\ntake diagonal. Default: 0.dim2(int,optional) – second dimension with respect to which to\ntake diagonal. Default: 1."
